## Technical Deep Dive (Key Algorithms)

**MCP Catalog Deduplication:**
```go
func CanonicalURL(raw string) string {
    // Strip tracking params, normalize protocol, lowercase host
    u, _ := url.Parse(raw)
    q := u.Query()
    // Remove known tracking params
    for _, tk := range []string{"utm_source", "utm_medium", "ref", "fbclid"} {
        q.Del(tk)
    }
    u.RawQuery = q.Encode()
    u.Fragment = ""
    u.Path = strings.TrimRight(u.Path, "/")
    return strings.ToLower(u.String())
}
```

